Chatterbox TTS on NVIDIA Jetson
Copyright 2026 Simon (muttleydosomething)

This project was developed collaboratively by Simon and Claude (Anthropic's
Claude Opus 4.6 via Claude Code). The SBSA library discovery, fp16 memory
optimization, and cuFFT workarounds were developed through an extended
debugging session spanning three days.

